  <p><b><span id="CSI_Manager">CSI Manager - Process Owner</span></b> </p>
  <ul>
    <li>The Continual Service Improvement (CSI) Manager is responsible for managing improvements to IT Service Management processes and IT services. He will continually measure the performance of the service provider and design improvements to processes, services and infrastructure in order to increase efficiency, effectiveness, and cost effectiveness.</li>
  </ul>
